| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0376 — Recovery Inhibition (alphv)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: b1c97dd5-89ab-5d65-a3b7-82f107e9a2b7"
